---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About NeuroLoop</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg">
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>NeuroLoop</strong>! I'm passionate about breaking down complex topics in 
        <strong>technology</strong> and <strong>artificial intelligence</strong> into simple, digestible content.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What I Do</h2>
      <p>
        I create educational videos that explore the cutting edge of tech, from AI and machine learning 
        to neurotechnology and beyond. My goal is to make advanced concepts accessible to everyone, 
        regardless of their background.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Topics I Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning</li>
        <li>Neurotechnology & Brain-Computer Interfaces</li>
        <li>Emerging Tech & Innovation</li>
        <li>Tech Explanations & Tutorials</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>
        I share regular updates and deep dives on my YouTube channel. 
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@neuroloop98" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Subscribe to stay updated
        </a> 
        with the latest content.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have a topic you'd like me to cover? Found a mistake in one of my videos? 
        Just want to say hi? Feel free to reach out through YouTube comments or social media.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-card rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Subscribe to NeuroLoop</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-6">Never miss a new video - join the community today!</p>
      <a 
        href="https://www.youtube.com/@neuroloop98" 
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium text-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Subscribe on YouTube
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-card mt-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-center text-muted">
      <p>Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} NeuroLoop. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
